Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:25.87,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,240)\blur4\bord4\3c&H4EAFED&\1a&HFF&}明明都懂 但就是無法除盡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:30.37,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,240)\blur4\bord4\3c&H4EAFED&\1a&HFF&}互相平行的心開始交叉
