Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED「ハニーシトロン」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:36.72,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}初めての恋が芽吹いた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:40.34,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}淡くゆれるココロとカラダ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:43.76,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}青くてスウィートな季節
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:47.10,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}あふれ出したハニーシトロン
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:50.44,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}気づかないふりはやめてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:53.90,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}ミルクティーンはもうおしまい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:57.44,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}ままごとでも知りたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:21:01.07,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}半分だけじゃもう足りない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:08.75,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}あぁ　予感も答えもまだ真っ白なままで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:11.63,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}背のびしてみるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:15.42,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}だってもっと近づきたい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:17.84,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}曖昧で割り切れない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:22.14,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}君の態度にやきもきしては
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:24.68,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}簡単に止められない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:29.14,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}瞬きの隙間さえ miss you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:31.56,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}やっぱ振り向かせたい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:35.98,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}今日も誓う鏡の奥で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:38.40,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}ちょっと切ないくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:43.16,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}何度だって君を夢見てる
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.46,0:20:36.72,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}情竇初開
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.72,0:20:40.34,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}身心恍恍蕩蕩
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.55,0:20:43.76,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}湛藍而甜蜜的季節
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.97,0:20:47.10,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}滿溢而出的蜂蜜檸檬水
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.10,0:20:50.44,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}請你不要視而不見
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.44,0:20:53.90,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}我們不再是乳臭未乾的小孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.23,0:20:57.44,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}即便是扮家家酒我也想知道
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.69,0:21:01.07,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}只有一半已經不能滿足
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.32,0:21:08.75,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}啊 沒有預感 沒有答案
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.96,0:21:11.63,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}試著踮起腳尖
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.63,0:21:15.42,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}因為我想離你更近
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.42,0:21:17.84,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}曖昧不清 無法割捨
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.84,0:21:22.14,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}你的態度令我焦慮不安
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.34,0:21:24.68,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}難以平復
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.68,0:21:29.14,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}眨眼間也是想念你
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.14,0:21:31.56,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}想讓你回頭看向我
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.56,0:21:35.98,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}今天也對著鏡子暗暗發誓
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.98,0:21:38.40,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}感覺鬱鬱寡歡
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.40,0:21:43.16,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}你在我心中 魂牽夢縈
